title: Unspecified error occurred?
body:
I tried downloading league of legends twice and all I get is 
Update Failed
Unspecified error occurred. Please check the logs for more information.
Please help!

replies.body:
Hey there,

Could you please reply with your latest patcher and launcher logs, these can be found in the directory listed below

Windows

>C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\Logs\Patcher Logs

Mac

>Applications/League of Legends/Logs/Patcher Logs

You can upload them to your site of choice or alternatively the [wrenchmen.org uploader](http://wrenchmen.org/upload/).

Oh wait don't worry! Fixed!
I accidentally changed my calendar date by -2 years.
That would also cause it, haha.
